{
  "id": "6a03f33fbf2edde1b3c5122b",
  "title": "服を見てから活動開始といきますか、、",
  "created": 1778643776,
  "updated": 1778643814,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a03f33fbf2edde1b3c5122b",
      "text": "服を見てから活動開始といきますか、、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa522d",
      "text": "from [2024/03/02]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa522e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643780
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa522f",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5230",
      "text": "　服を見てから活動開始といきますか、、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5231",
      "text": "  [https://www.fashion-press.net/collections/20018 ロエベ(LOEWE) 2024-25年秋冬ウィメンズコレクション - ファッションプレス]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5232",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/dd583885984873247d218f3c666a841b][https://gyazo.com/e8592219b979ee1d3508f7fc59988e78]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5233",
      "text": "   とんでもないきれいさだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5234",
      "text": "   このデニム(？よくわからない)は実用的な意味で手元に欲しい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5235",
      "text": "   \tまずい、これめっちゃ欲しくなってきた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5236",
      "text": "   \tこれヤバイな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5237",
      "text": "   \tどこかドメブラが似たようなものを作って無さそうなこともない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5238",
      "text": "   \t\tいくつか調べてたらまあまあ近いものが出てきた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5239",
      "text": "   \t\t[https://gyazo.com/a4b71ada46989ae88cdae2563c01b28a]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa523a",
      "text": "   \t\t安い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa523b",
      "text": "   \t\tやはりLOEWEは圧倒的にいい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa523c",
      "text": "   \tすごく欲しい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa523d",
      "text": "   バックルがでかくてビックルになってしまう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa523e",
      "text": "  [https://www.fashion-press.net/collections/20017 イッセイ ミヤケ(ISSEY MIYAKE) 2024-25年秋冬ウィメンズコレクション - ファッションプレス]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa523f",
      "text": "  \t非常にかっこいい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5240",
      "text": "　\t[https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/fall-2024-ready-to-wear/vetements Vetements Fall 2024 Ready-to-Wear Collection | Vogue]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5241",
      "text": "  \tもったいつけた割に？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5242",
      "text": "  \tこのむっくりした感じをかっこいいと思わなくなってきた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5243",
      "text": "  何日か前だけどアンリアレイジ24AW面白",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5244",
      "text": "  \tパリでやっていたのか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5245",
      "text": "  \t[https://www.fashion-press.net/collections/19972 アンリアレイジ(ANREALAGE) 2024-25年秋冬ウィメンズコレクション - ファッションプレス]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5246",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/b825f8f4dcc25f26322daa54f764b1ea]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5247",
      "text": "    [ドラえもん]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5248",
      "text": "\t\t\t服とは",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa5249",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/0e2ca88f80923d1681e3b0dfa992ba8f]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa524a",
      "text": "\t\t\t[抽象化されたジャイアン]草",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa524b",
      "text": "\t\t\tタケコプターってネーミングなかなか狂っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa524c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[https://www.wikiwand.com/ja/タケコプター タケコプター - Wikiwand]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03f3400000000000aa524d",
      "text": "    ツッコミどころ満載で面白い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778643776,
      "updated": 1778643776
    },
    {
